Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.00,0:01:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十話\N復仇的惡鬼\N志志雄真正的謀略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.68,0:01:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看你往哪逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.96,0:02:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.23,0:02:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為這樣 我就殺不了你了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.64,0:02:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種手刺突劍法 出奇不意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.51,0:02:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能讓敵人無法招架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.15,0:02:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是新撰組副隊長 土方歲三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.68,0:02:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所發明的劍法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.99,0:02:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我的牙突劍法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.22,0:02:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比他更厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.49,0:02:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是牙突劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.17,0:02:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自以為是的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.61,0:02:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我從十年前到現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.85,0:02:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,經過無數次危難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.15,0:03:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所練出來的劍法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.92,0:03:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看你能如何招架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.79,0:03:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.93,0:03:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.37,0:03:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.21,0:03:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然緋村胸部已受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.15,0:03:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他第二次的反擊\N會比第一次快速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我猜的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.95,0:03:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙\N已慢慢燃起決鬥的戰火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.99,0:03:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過還未完全恢復從前的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.64,0:04:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比我預期的還要快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.68,0:04:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心的呼吸愈來愈快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.17,0:04:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果他全力以赴 和我決鬥的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.01,0:04:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就得使出 真正的牙突劍法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.02,0:04:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在才是真正的牙突劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.21,0:05:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒 牙突劍這麼簡單就被打挎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.01,0:05:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤 你在京都和我決戰時\N用的就是這一招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.45,0:05:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到過了十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.26,0:05:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一點長進也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.36,0:05:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在這一招對我 已完全沒有作用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.00,0:05:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起來 我們的決鬥還沒結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.10,0:05:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決鬥 我現在不想和你決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要讓你死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.71,0:05:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這句話該是我說才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.32,0:05:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.39,0:05:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 又變回過去的他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.86,0:06:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.43,0:06:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阻止他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再這樣下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.53,0:06:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心會消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.54,0:07:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一次是你的人頭 落地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.54,0:07:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手 誰來阻止他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰 別費神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.35,0:07:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.68,0:07:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們無法阻止他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.42,0:07:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心現在已回到從前的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.19,0:07:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在幕府的京都中戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.69,0:07:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他聽不到我們的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有決一死戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.33,0:07:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分出勝負 他們才會停手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.38,0:07:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,川路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.88,0:07:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.04,0:08:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤進入道場多久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已四個小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.02,0:08:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們快去阻止他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.06,0:08:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚了就來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.43,0:08:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.37,0:08:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刀折斷了還能用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.70,0:08:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是牙突劍法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.04,0:08:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是新撰組的成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.61,0:08:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新撰組家規第一條\N士可殺不可辱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.55,0:08:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕不允許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.35,0:08:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臨陣脫逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.02,0:08:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒武器了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.92,0:08:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下劍心贏定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.25,0:08:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死到臨頭還嘴硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.59,0:08:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙還想赤手抵擋劍心\N看他有多大能耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.53,0:08:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,制服的皮帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.37,0:09:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.24,0:09:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了 沒有劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.91,0:09:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心勝算就不大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.25,0:09:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我讓你死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.72,0:09:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心會被勒死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.22,0:09:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想勒斷劍心的脖子\N沒那麼容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.62,0:09:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是武士的決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.91,0:09:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是幕府式的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.01,0:09:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二人都在做最後的一擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.98,0:09:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論生死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.45,0:09:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都要拚個你死我活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.55,0:09:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就快分出勝負了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.03,0:09:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也該結束了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.70,0:09:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.16,0:10:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.63,0:10:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤 住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.33,0:10:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別忘了你的任務\N只是測知緋村劍心的實力而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.47,0:10:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧 既然警察督長這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.54,0:10:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警察督長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.94,0:10:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,測知實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.38,0:10:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.01,0:10:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤 我知道你武功高強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.85,0:10:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我想你也不願意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.59,0:10:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看緋村劍心就此白白犧牲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.89,0:11:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來 真正的幕後指使者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是你這個薩摩藩維新志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.66,0:11:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明治政府內務省長\N大久保利道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.27,0:11:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大久保利道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.71,0:11:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這些人究竟在講什麼\N我怎麼一句也聽不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.45,0:11:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼不懂少廢話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.25,0:11:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.18,0:11:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明治維新的三位領導人 西鄉隆盛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桂小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.39,0:11:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及目前僅存的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.13,0:11:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這位大久保先生嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.73,0:11:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在則是日本最高大臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.17,0:11:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒想到會造成今天的局面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.61,0:11:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我真正的目的\N只是想測知你們的實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.88,0:11:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我有不得已的苦衷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.58,0:11:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不快說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.69,0:11:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.72,0:12:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來就是這個超級大人物\N大久保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.52,0:12:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回去向涉海老大稟告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.50,0:12:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正下次有的是機會\N我再找你決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.64,0:12:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算你命大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.34,0:12:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.14,0:12:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 齊藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤向你報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.64,0:12:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村劍心只不過是個\N虛有其表的窩囊廢罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.91,0:12:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法勝任大任 以上報告完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.05,0:12:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙雖是警察廳的密探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.62,0:12:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但卻讓人捉摸不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.99,0:12:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村 外頭備有馬車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.33,0:12:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.50,0:12:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有話現在直說就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.03,0:12:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想知道整件事的不只是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.92,0:13:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在場的每一個都有權利知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.42,0:13:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在場的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.16,0:13:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有話就快說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.86,0:13:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心又恢復清醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.07,0:13:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.17,0:13:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼啊 大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.97,0:13:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥 還不快去拿藥箱來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.47,0:13:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.21,0:13:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心你別這樣\N大久保大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.14,0:13:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.81,0:13:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我們也只能\N順從他的意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.38,0:13:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就直說吧 緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.65,0:13:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄現正在京都為非作亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.09,0:13:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大久保先生 誰又是志志雄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.96,0:13:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你少插嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.17,0:13:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄和我一樣\N都是武士出身的殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.30,0:13:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄屬於長州派的維新志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.04,0:14:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我不同的是\N他專搞地下活動從不出面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.21,0:14:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此大家就稱他\N影子殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.82,0:14:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時大家也都認為\N他是我的繼承者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.35,0:14:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.92,0:14:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼承者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.45,0:14:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.59,0:14:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此包括我在內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.63,0:14:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幾乎沒人見過\N他的廬山真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.50,0:14:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳說志志雄在十年前\N戊辰戰爭中戰死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.24,0:14:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但其實\N他是被同志給殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.08,0:14:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是為確保國家安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.12,0:14:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不得已採取的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.82,0:14:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然 志志雄的武功和你不相上下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.99,0:14:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他卻是一個名利薰心的危險人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.17,0:15:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於維新志士們非常瞭解 志志雄的實力與價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.81,0:15:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以暗殺的計劃無法公開\N否則必會造成日本的大混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.38,0:15:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但如果不除掉他 日本就會被其操控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.89,0:15:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玩弄於股掌間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.69,0:15:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.66,0:15:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們就趁著戊辰戰爭時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.46,0:15:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將他殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.39,0:15:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本想放火燒死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.37,0:15:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到他雖然全身燒灼 卻死裏逃生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.31,0:15:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從那時候起 志志雄就化為復仇魔鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.08,0:15:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為喜好戰鬥 破壞和平的武器商人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.15,0:15:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在其領導下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.99,0:15:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在京都的黑街內 組成一支龐大的地下兵團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.99,0:16:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顛覆日本 分化這個國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.53,0:16:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是他的復仇計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.83,0:16:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們好幾次派出平反的軍隊\N卻全被他打敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.77,0:16:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在只有靠你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.54,0:16:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.61,0:16:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了國家與人民\N你一定要回京都一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.05,0:16:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.55,0:16:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是要劍心 去刺殺志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.03,0:16:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.53,0:16:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然 我們會付出龐大的報酬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.16,0:16:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且對你們過去的違法行為 也既往不究
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.30,0:16:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比方說 我們不會抓小惠小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.14,0:16:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑\N你們休想拿我來威脅劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.18,0:16:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則我寧願去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.68,0:17:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這群卑鄙的小人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.06,0:17:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們休想拿虛偽的理由 逼劍心就範
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.16,0:17:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心既然決定不再殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.66,0:17:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在也不會再為你們殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.37,0:17:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這關係到國家存亡的危機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.14,0:17:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無能的政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.70,0:17:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不都是你們這群人造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.17,0:17:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政府的繁榮\N人民的和平就看這次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.91,0:17:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是你們家的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.08,0:17:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再胡說我就逮捕你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.28,0:17:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,試試看呀 你這狗官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.15,0:17:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我不知道你們在吵什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.75,0:17:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要殺志志雄是你們的事 別來找劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.56,0:17:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們可別一意孤行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.13,0:17:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大久保大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.40,0:17:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你們需要劍心的幫助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.64,0:17:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他現在已決定\N收手不再殺人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.24,0:17:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也絕不讓他到京都去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.78,0:17:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.48,0:17:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕不讓他去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.85,0:18:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心是我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.35,0:18:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會守著劍心的\N無論發生什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.38,0:18:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.82,0:18:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,國家的命運 就要毀於你們手裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 川路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.36,0:18:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大久保大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.06,0:18:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們可以再考慮看看 不必急著回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.31,0:18:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大久保利通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.44,0:18:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.38,0:18:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來 齊藤是大久保的走狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.95,0:18:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 只要我揭發這個秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就可以做下任的內務卿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.12,0:18:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.82,0:18:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大久保是何等的超級大人物\N我還想保住我的小命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.29,0:18:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就別再拖我下水\N讓我到上海去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.94,0:18:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看你上海也別去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.54,0:19:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地獄更適合你去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.42,0:19:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,涉海 你還是一點都沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.25,0:19:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你表面假裝是維新志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.46,0:19:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,骨子裏卻在完成自己的私慾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.43,0:19:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是有你這種敗類 國家才會大亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.53,0:19:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的工作就是為政府做密探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.63,0:19:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,專門找出像你這種該殺的敗類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.47,0:19:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是新撰組的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.78,0:19:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有害國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.28,0:19:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就要除惡務盡 絕不饒赦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.89,0:19:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 我可以給你錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.82,0:19:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狗有飼料就行 人可以用錢買通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.46,0:19:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是卻買不到正義的大野狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.00,0:20:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去是 現在也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.60,0:20:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新撰組就是新撰組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大野狼就是大野狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.34,0:20:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍客就是劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.58,0:20:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧 緋村劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.96,0:20:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一星期後的五月十四日 我會再來找你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.74,0:20:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧 就等五月十四日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.74,0:20:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大久保先生 你比十年前消瘦了不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.95,0:20:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了國家的前途 這是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.89,0:21:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會等你們的好消息的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.94,0:21:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.07,0:21:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我們見到大久保大人的最後一夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.14,0:21:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明治十一年五月十四日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.62,0:21:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我們人生的轉折點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.58,0:21:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它將改變我們每個人的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.26,0:21:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但現在誰也不知道究竟會如何

